<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Moments of Mine</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: #f7f8fc;
      color: #1f2937;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #111827, #2563eb);
      color: white;
      padding: 70px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    header p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      max-width: 650px;
      margin: 0 auto 30px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: white;
      color: #2563eb;
      padding: 14px 24px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: 0.2s ease;
    }

    .button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    nav {
      background: white;
      padding: 18px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 10;
    }

    nav a {
      color: #374151;
      margin: 0 15px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    section {
      padding: 70px 20px;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    section h2 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .intro {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 750px;
      margin: 0 auto 45px;
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    .cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 25px;
    }

    .card {
      background: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07);
      transition: 0.2s ease;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: #2563eb;
    }

    .about {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 45px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    }

    .contact-box {
      text-align: center;
      background: #111827;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 50px 25px;
    }

    .contact-box a {
      color: white;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      background: #e5e7eb;
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      header h1 {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
      }

      nav a {
        display: inline-block;
        margin: 8px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav>
    <a href="#services">Services</a>
    <a href="#about">About</a>
    <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
  </nav>

  <header>
    <h1>Your Business Name</h1>
    <p>A clean, professional website built for free using GitHub Pages. Replace this text with what you do and who you help.</p>
    <a class="button" href="#contact">Get in Touch</a>
  </header>

  <section id="services">
    <h2>What I Do</h2>
    <p class="intro">Use this section to explain your services, skills, products, or offer. Keep it simple and clear.</p>

    <div class="cards">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Service One</h3>
        <p>Describe your first service here. For example: website design, social media help, consulting, tutoring, repairs, or digital products.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Service Two</h3>
        <p>Describe your second service here. Focus on the benefit to the customer, not just the feature.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Service Three</h3>
        <p>Describe your third service here. Short, simple descriptions usually work best.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="about">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <div class="about">
      <p>Hello, I’m <strong>Your Name</strong>. I help people with <strong>your main skill or service</strong>. This website is a simple place to show what I offer, build trust, and make it easy for people to contact me.</p>
      <br />
      <p>Replace this section with a short story about who you are, what you do, and why someone should choose you.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact">
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <div class="contact-box">
      <p>Interested in working together?</p>
      <p>Email me at: <a href="mailto:your@email.com">your@email.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 Your Business Name. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
